  ('Rare_4', 'Guardian Angel', 'Rare', 'Start adventures with +1 Revive Last Breath: If it''s the first time I''ve been slain this game, revive me with 1 Health.', 'https://dd.b.pvp.net/6_12_0/adventure/en_us/img/relics/R0007.png'),
